# Updraft — Premium Youth-Led NGO Website Plan

A cinematic, dark-mode, editorial landing page for Updraft. Real logo integrated. Single-page long-scroll with 9 sections. Built on the existing TanStack Start + Tailwind v4 template.

---

## 1. Design System

- **Palette (dark-first)**: near-black background `#0A0A0B`, charcoal surfaces `#111111`, deep navy `#0B1220` for depth. Foreground soft white `#F4F4F0`. Accent: muted Updraft sage green from the logo, registered as `--accent`.
- **Typography**: Inter (body) + a distinctive display weight for editorial headlines. Tight tracking on large type. Lucide icons throughout.
- **Motion**: scroll-reveal fade + translate, soft animated green glow in hero, hover glow borders on cards. Restrained, not excessive.
- **CSS tokens** in `src/styles.css` mapped to Tailwind classes: `--background`, `--foreground`, `--surface`, `--surface-elevated`, `--border`, `--muted`, `--accent`, `--accent-soft`, `--accent-glow`.

