## 3. Page Structure (Single Route)

Route: `src/routes/index.tsx`. Sticky navbar with hash links. Smooth scroll + `scroll-margin-top`.

| # | Section | Key Content |
|---|---------|-------------|
| 1 | **Navbar** | Logo left. Links: Mission · Skills · Program · Team · Get Involved · Contact. "Volunteer" CTA right. Translucent + backdrop-blur on scroll. |
| 2 | **Hero** | Full viewport. Eyebrow: "A Youth-Led Organization · India". H1: "Lifting youth, elevating communities." Sub: "Inculcating 21st century skills in India's youth." Two CTAs: "Confidence Building Bootcamp" → `#program`, "Volunteer" → form. Background: generated cinematic image of Indian youth, dark gradient overlay, subtle green glow, fine grain. |
| 3 | **Mission** | Editorial two-column. Pull quote: "Education taught them to memorize. We teach them to lead." + closing mission statement. |
| 4 | **21st Century Skills** | Responsive grid: Leadership, Communication, Confidence, Teamwork, Creativity, Critical Thinking, Digital Literacy, Emotional Intelligence. Lucide icon + title + short copy + hover glow border. |
| 5 | **Confidence Building Bootcamp** (`#program`) | **Flagship premium editorial layout**. Oversized featured card, cinematic visuals, modern typography, highlighted outcomes, elegant spacing, subtle motion. |
| 6 | **Team** | 6 circular monogram avatars with green ring: Prince Rathore, Aanya Mishra, Samyukta Sharma, Tvisha Malhotra, Shaurya Jain, Maira Rajput. |
| 7 | **Get Involved** | "Pick your way in." 3 cards: Volunteer, School Partnership, Sponsor & Collaborate. |
| 8 | **Contact** | Email, phone, Instagram. "Usually replies within 24 hours." |
| 9 | **Footer** | Logo, explore links, Instagram icon, "India", copyright. |

