## 4. Confidence Building Bootcamp — Detailed Spec

**Emotional tone:** Growth, confidence, self-expression, leadership, practical learning, real transformation.

**Layout:** Premium editorial oversized featured card spanning full width on desktop, with:
- Cinematic hero visual (left or background) of online youth workshop / speaking environment
- Title: **Confidence Building Bootcamp**
- Key details row: 19th & 20th June 2026 · Online via Google Meet · Free · Limited to 100
- Description paragraph aligned with Updraft vision
- "What you'll gain" outcomes in a clean list/grid with green accent markers
- Program structure: Day 1 = Interactive Training Session, Day 2 = Confidence Competition
- Outcomes list: Exclusive Confidence Cheat Sheet, Certificate of Participation, Certificate of Achievement, LoR for winners, LoA for winners, 3-Month Mentorship for winners, Social Media Recognition, better public speaking/communication, leadership & self-expression, real confidence for MUNs/interviews/debates/presentations
- CTA: **"Apply Now"** → `https://forms.gle/bmU5qMhLfNz7VA1z6`

**Visual treatment:**
- Dark surface card with subtle border glow on hover
- Cinematic generated image of TED-style youth speaking / virtual workshop
- Outcomes presented as clean tag-like pills or icon list
- Generous whitespace, large type for the title, elegant hierarchy
- Subtle entrance animation (fade-up on scroll)

