## 6. Technical Details

- Update `src/routes/__root.tsx` head with Updraft title, description, OG tags, favicon.
- New components under `src/components/sections/`: `Navbar`, `Hero`, `Mission`, `Skills`, `Program`, `Team`, `GetInvolved`, `Contact`, `Footer`.
- Shared: `SectionEyebrow`, `RevealOnScroll` (IntersectionObserver + CSS).
- Reveal via IO hook + Tailwind keyframes. No new heavy deps.
- `html { scroll-behavior: smooth }` + `scroll-mt-24` on anchors.
- Mobile-first responsive.

